255
00:11:17,599 --> 00:11:19,339
- Where are we delivering it?
- Yeah!

256
00:11:20,336 --> 00:11:21,776
Just around the…

257
00:11:21,801 --> 00:11:23,309
That’s too far!

258
00:11:23,334 --> 00:11:24,944
We might get lost!

259
00:11:24,969 --> 00:11:29,564
I haven’t even said anything yet!

260
00:11:30,758 --> 00:11:32,771
Don’t take off your hat!

261
00:11:32,796 --> 00:11:34,690
Oh come on, that’s on you!
Come here, you!

262
00:11:36,807 --> 00:11:38,153
Hey, whose car is this?!

263
00:11:38,824 --> 00:11:39,824
It’s beautiful!

264
00:11:40,201 --> 00:11:41,628
It’s a brand new car!

265
00:11:41,672 --> 00:11:42,945
Whose is this?

266
00:11:43,345 --> 00:11:45,152
It’s… it’s… red!

267
00:11:45,331 --> 00:11:47,251
- It’s beautiful!
- It’s white!

268
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,640
This is not red!

269
00:11:49,383 --> 00:11:50,637
It’s so nice!

270
00:11:50,662 --> 00:11:53,198
- Hey! Stop that!
- Kuya…

271
00:11:53,223 --> 00:11:55,930
You might scratch the car,
it’s brand new!

272
00:11:56,021 --> 00:11:57,728
- It’s so smooth!
- Here, look!

273
00:11:57,845 --> 00:11:59,838
- It’s so smooth!
- Hey!

274
00:12:00,069 --> 00:12:01,195
Why are you diving in there?!

275
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:02,220
Whose is this?!

276
00:12:02,535 --> 00:12:03,795
I was just touching it!

277
00:12:03,921 --> 00:12:05,268
And what if you scratch it?

278
00:12:05,576 --> 00:12:07,263
- That’s brand new!
- Is this yours?!

279
00:12:08,126 --> 00:12:10,837
- You’re unbelievable!
- It’s his?!

280
00:12:10,912 --> 00:12:13,292
Tso K, here’s the key!

281
00:12:13,525 --> 00:12:15,436
- Big time!
- I’ll go ahead now!

282
00:12:16,208 --> 00:12:18,482
Enjoy, and congrats on the new car!

283
00:12:18,737 --> 00:12:20,243
Thank you, raffle girl!

284
00:12:20,507 --> 00:12:22,500
You’re legit!

285
00:12:22,738 --> 00:12:23,905
Wooh!

286
00:12:23,986 --> 00:12:26,100
- Thank you, thank you!
- Uh, miss, miss, miss!

287
00:12:28,183 --> 00:12:30,543
Why are you always wearing that?

288
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:32,520
Don’t you have clothes or shorts?

289
00:12:32,693 --> 00:12:33,839
I have them, but this is the vibe.

290
00:12:34,465 --> 00:12:36,607
- That’s the vibe?
- Oh! Alright, thanks!

291
00:12:36,644 --> 00:12:38,438
I told you to change for the better.

292
00:12:38,463 --> 00:12:40,280
You’re really something else!

293
00:12:40,305 --> 00:12:41,763
- Why?
- I mean, look at you!

294
00:12:41,788 --> 00:12:44,534
- Wow!
- Did you really win this?!

295
00:12:44,565 --> 00:12:45,785
The headlights are so cool!

296
00:12:45,810 --> 00:12:47,651
Oh no. I’m just really lucky.

297
00:12:47,676 --> 00:12:51,142
You know, they say when
you’re a good person,

298
00:12:51,166 --> 00:12:52,598
- you get lucky.
- That’s true.

299
00:12:52,623 --> 00:12:56,522
But if you, Iskineport,
steal your friend’s partner...

300
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:58,321
- Me?
- That’s when you’ll get unlucky!

301
00:12:58,345 --> 00:12:59,345
Right, BFF?

302
00:12:59,873 --> 00:13:03,586
Not true! No one’s stealing from you!
Here you go again!

303
00:13:03,611 --> 00:13:05,348
I was just saying!
I’m not targeting anyone!

304
00:13:05,373 --> 00:13:08,300
- Forget it! Let’s go test drive!
- What test drive?

305
00:13:08,371 --> 00:13:10,257
- Let’s try it!
- Wow! Try?!

306
00:13:10,282 --> 00:13:11,457
- Hey!
- So we can try it!

307
00:13:11,482 --> 00:13:13,934
What do you think this is,
a delivery van?!

308
00:13:14,152 --> 00:13:15,152
- A delivery van!
- Wow!

309
00:13:15,170 --> 00:13:16,536
- Yes!
- It’s beautiful!

310
00:13:16,561 --> 00:13:18,182
- Oh, don’t–
- Don’t touch it!

311
00:13:18,586 --> 00:13:20,533
Wow! It looks so fancy!

312
00:13:20,558 --> 00:13:22,183
Why are you–
My love, don’t touch it!

313
00:13:22,208 --> 00:13:23,842
It’s not just that, not just that!
Look at the lights!

314
00:13:23,867 --> 00:13:29,051
Oh, yeah, wow, the lights are beautiful!
The car’s amazing, I want to–

315
00:13:29,076 --> 00:13:30,076
My love!

316
00:13:30,826 --> 00:13:32,248
- I could sleep here!
- I’m so jealous!

317
00:13:32,897 --> 00:13:35,304
We really need to test drive that!

318
00:13:35,329 --> 00:13:38,691
That was gre–great acting, Pokwang!

319
00:13:38,716 --> 00:13:40,231
Let’s go!

320
00:13:42,352 --> 00:13:44,318
- My love, my love, my love!
- What?

321
00:13:44,763 --> 00:13:46,196
You’re the only one
who gets to hug it.

322
00:13:46,221 --> 00:13:47,640
- You’re the only one who gets to touch it!
- He won’t let anyone touch it!

323
00:13:47,665 --> 00:13:50,282
No, we really need to test drive it!

324
00:13:50,345 --> 00:13:52,438
- Perfect timing, Chef K...
- Hmm?

325
00:13:52,515 --> 00:13:56,651
My love needs to pick up supplies,
can you maybe go with him?

326
00:13:56,676 --> 00:13:57,770
See? I told you!

327
00:13:58,074 --> 00:13:59,740
That’s what I told him!
He didn’t want to!

328
00:13:59,765 --> 00:14:01,338
- Huh?
- I’ve been asking to

329
00:14:01,362 --> 00:14:04,008
- help deliver supplies!
- But you said you didn’t want to?

330
00:14:04,033 --> 00:14:05,779
I didn’t say that! Just agree!

331
00:14:05,916 --> 00:14:06,973
- Oh, so you’re coming with me?
- Before I change my mind.

332
00:14:06,998 --> 00:14:08,223
Okay, alright, let’s go!

333
00:14:08,313 --> 00:14:09,793
Alright! Let’s go!

334
00:14:09,818 --> 00:14:11,348
Thanks, Chef K!

335
00:14:11,373 --> 00:14:12,821
- Of course! Let’s go! Hop in!
- Take care!

336
00:14:12,846 --> 00:14:14,551
- Let’s go!
- Alright!

337
00:14:14,629 --> 00:14:15,975
I’m so jealous,
you got to touch it!

338
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:18,482
It’s really different!

339
00:14:18,507 --> 00:14:21,787
Oh! Be careful!

340
00:14:22,017 --> 00:14:23,977
Don’t sit too fast!

341
00:14:24,235 --> 00:14:25,961
- Ow!
- Why’s it like that?!

342
00:14:26,205 --> 00:14:32,010
Don’t be too heavy,
you’re going to deform the foam!

343
00:14:37,752 --> 00:14:40,285
We have the subject here.

344
00:14:43,913 --> 00:14:44,913
This is amazing!

345
00:14:45,417 --> 00:14:46,910
This is really something else!

346
00:14:49,478 --> 00:14:52,025
This is really something else!

347
00:14:52,205 --> 00:14:53,205
Of course!

348
00:14:53,679 --> 00:14:55,026
It’s so gorgeous!

349
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,240
Isn’t it?

350
00:14:56,508 --> 00:14:57,548
You’re so lucky!

351
00:14:57,573 --> 00:14:58,573
Thank you!

352
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:01,910
- I wish we joined the raffle!
- The supplies, get the supplies!

353
00:15:04,145 --> 00:15:05,145
It’s so gorgeous!

354
00:15:05,622 --> 00:15:06,929
This is really something else!

355
00:15:08,561 --> 00:15:10,615
No, it really is!
He’s got an awesome new ride!

356
00:15:11,093 --> 00:15:12,186
Next level kinda thing!

357
00:15:12,211 --> 00:15:13,407
- Amazing. So, so cool!
- Because it’s new!

358
00:15:13,578 --> 00:15:14,578
- What?
- It’s new, it’s new!

359
00:15:14,655 --> 00:15:16,002
It’s so cool!
You can’t even feel the bump –

360
00:15:16,027 --> 00:15:17,549
Everybody, hands up!
This is the police!

361
00:15:18,757 --> 00:15:20,470
We’re placing you
under arrest for carnapping.

362
00:15:20,983 --> 00:15:22,356
- Carnapping?
- Carnapping!

363
00:15:22,587 --> 00:15:23,587
How is this carnapping?

364
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,267
- This is his car!
- What?

365
00:15:25,446 --> 00:15:26,799
How is this carnapping?
Isn’t this yours?

366
00:15:26,866 --> 00:15:28,012
Look, he has the keys!

367
00:15:28,134 --> 00:15:29,181
Yeah,
but just because I drove the car!

368
00:15:29,206 --> 00:15:31,445
That’s enough, we’ve heard enough!
We’ll take your statements at the precinct.

369
00:15:31,889 --> 00:15:33,442
- Whoa, whoa, whoa! Wait!
- What… how is this happening?

370
00:15:33,706 --> 00:15:34,774
How is this happening?

371
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:36,483
How is this carnapping?
I just won it!

372
00:15:36,521 --> 00:15:37,687
Where are the papers for it?

373
00:15:38,189 --> 00:15:39,533
The... I have no idea.

374
00:15:39,558 --> 00:15:41,831
- Wait... just hold on, boss.
- I don’t know about any papers…

375
00:15:41,856 --> 00:15:45,583
This is just a misunderstanding.
My husband is not a carnapper.

376
00:15:45,771 --> 00:15:47,311
Boss, boss, just a moment.

377
00:15:47,759 --> 00:15:51,019
Look at this guy,
he’s drowning in debt!

378
00:15:51,044 --> 00:15:53,804
How could he possibly
afford a car like this?!

379
00:15:53,829 --> 00:15:56,353
Thank you so much, Lola Maxi,
thank you!

380
00:15:56,546 --> 00:15:58,748
Boss! Maybe we can
talk this over?

381
00:15:59,261 --> 00:16:00,634
I have some snacks money here.

382
00:16:01,048 --> 00:16:02,048
You’re dead meat.

383
00:16:02,321 --> 00:16:03,876
- What?!
- Are you trying to bribe us?

384
00:16:04,049 --> 00:16:05,357
- Huh?
- That’s a new case.

385
00:16:05,382 --> 00:16:06,391
- Yeah!
- Bribery!

386
00:16:06,535 --> 00:16:07,733
- Dead meat right away?
- Let’s go, let’s go!

387
00:16:07,758 --> 00:16:08,886
I told you...

388
00:16:08,911 --> 00:16:10,698
Let’s go, let’s go to the station

389
00:16:10,886 --> 00:16:12,371
- Wait a second!
- Come with us!

390
00:16:12,396 --> 00:16:15,453
Wh–what?! Why is this happening?
I just won the car, that’s all. Ow!

391
00:16:17,809 --> 00:16:20,336
These are the two car thieves
we caught today.

392
00:16:20,361 --> 00:16:21,768
- Car thieves?!
- Car thieves?!

393
00:16:21,793 --> 00:16:25,077
That car was won by my BFF
in a raffle, right?!

394
00:16:25,243 --> 00:16:27,563
What raffle-raffle?!
That’s an old excuse!

395
00:16:27,594 --> 00:16:29,053
- Come on, get in there.
- Just go in!

396
00:16:29,078 --> 00:16:30,281
- Wait, hold on! Hold on!
- What?

397
00:16:30,623 --> 00:16:31,936
Tso K, BFF...

398
00:16:31,989 --> 00:16:34,111
- What?
- Does the car have papers?

399
00:16:34,218 --> 00:16:35,555
- It doesn’t.
- Then let’s go in.

400
00:16:38,199 --> 00:16:39,199
Let’s go inside.

401
00:16:40,123 --> 00:16:41,582
We’re sick of each other already!

402
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,720
Our t-shirts, though!

403
00:16:42,871 --> 00:16:43,871
Fine, fine.

404
00:16:44,017 --> 00:16:45,017
Okay!

405
00:16:45,721 --> 00:16:47,354
Here’s your new cellmate!

406
00:16:47,871 --> 00:16:49,238
- You take care of them!
- Wait, wait!

407
00:16:50,437 --> 00:16:52,250
What really happened
with that car?!

408
00:16:52,439 --> 00:16:54,119
- What?
- Why–why is this happening?!

409
00:16:54,149 --> 00:16:55,963
I just won it!
What did I do wrong?!

410
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,367
- Oh, so we don’t have any papers?
- None!

411
00:16:57,392 --> 00:16:59,146
- So no papers, that’s why we’re here.
- Alright, enough of that!

412
00:16:59,171 --> 00:17:00,594
- Okay, enough already.
- Change into your uniforms.

413
00:17:00,619 --> 00:17:01,648
- Here they are.
- Changing already?

414
00:17:02,208 --> 00:17:03,208
- Yes.
- Dress them up now!

415
00:17:03,265 --> 00:17:04,985
Change now!
Change now!

416
00:17:07,467 --> 00:17:09,992
- Don’t even turn your back, it’s fine!
- You’re really enjoying this, huh!

417
00:17:10,058 --> 00:17:11,378
They’re starting to brood.

418
00:17:11,866 --> 00:17:13,540
- Yeah, they really are.
- Why are you brooding? Huh?

419
00:17:14,298 --> 00:17:16,545
I told you this would happen.
Look what we got into.

420
00:17:16,570 --> 00:17:17,754
- My love!
- My love!

421
00:17:18,426 --> 00:17:20,486
- My love!
- Lola Maxi! Lola Maxi!

422
00:17:20,511 --> 00:17:21,511
- Are you okay?
- Cha!

423
00:17:21,536 --> 00:17:22,062
- Cha!
- My love!

424
00:17:22,121 --> 00:17:22,748
My love...

425
00:17:22,773 --> 00:17:25,319
What do you mean me?
It’s me! Don’t be like that…

426
00:17:25,447 --> 00:17:27,461
My love! My love,
I’m sorry, my love!

427
00:17:27,567 --> 00:17:29,014
- Are you okay?
- No, it’s just that...

428
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:31,804
- Why me?!
- Well, it’s your car, right?!

429
00:17:31,910 --> 00:17:33,670
- Yeah, but it’s not my fault!
- Exactly!

430
00:17:33,695 --> 00:17:35,894
It’s the first time I won something,
I had no idea. It was just a raffle!

431
00:17:35,919 --> 00:17:36,919
What really happened?

432
00:17:36,944 --> 00:17:41,518
That’s what I’m saying... just don’t...
please, don’t bring the kids here.

433
00:17:41,585 --> 00:17:43,243
- My love... Be strong.
- My love...

434
00:17:43,268 --> 00:17:44,589
- Yes, yes, yes, my love.
- I’ll be back, okay?

435
00:17:45,093 --> 00:17:46,319
We’ll get through this.

436
00:17:46,344 --> 00:17:47,948
Alright, Cha, okay?
Be careful, alright?

437
00:17:47,973 --> 00:17:49,281
- Alright.
- Let’s go.

438
00:17:49,305 --> 00:17:52,484
- Okay!
- Honestly, this is all your fault!

439
00:17:52,509 --> 00:17:54,206
- It’s not my fault!
- It’s your fault!

440
00:17:54,231 --> 00:17:55,808
You were the one who wanted
to test it, weren’t you?!

441
00:17:55,833 --> 00:17:57,418
And now it’s my fault?!

442
00:17:57,620 --> 00:17:59,560
What’s the noise all about?!

443
00:17:59,681 --> 00:18:00,681
What’s going on?!

444
00:18:00,706 --> 00:18:02,819
Can’t you see this prisoner
is deep in thought?!

445
00:18:05,138 --> 00:18:06,138
Nothing’s going on.

446
00:18:06,251 --> 00:18:08,191
- Okay, then shut up!
- He’s our mayor here.

447
00:18:09,089 --> 00:18:10,089
What?!

448
00:18:10,114 --> 00:18:11,281
- Hey!
- Hey!

449
00:18:11,596 --> 00:18:13,256
- Look who’s here! Huh?
- Tso K!

450
00:18:13,669 --> 00:18:15,955
I know you!
Stop acting all tough!

451
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:17,478
- Are you talking to me?
- You know him?

452
00:18:17,503 --> 00:18:18,503
I know you!

453
00:18:18,731 --> 00:18:20,191
This guy owes me a lot of money!

454
00:18:20,216 --> 00:18:21,216
- What?!
- What?!

455
00:18:21,241 --> 00:18:22,241
No—

456
00:18:22,266 --> 00:18:23,834
You’ve been hiding here all along!

457
00:18:23,859 --> 00:18:24,859
- Tso K...
- Huh?

458
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:25,950
And you dared to scream–

459
00:18:25,975 --> 00:18:27,800
You have credit to collect
even from here?!

460
00:18:27,825 --> 00:18:31,469
How would I know he’d show up here,
I didn’t think he’d get caught!

461
00:18:31,494 --> 00:18:33,014
You’ve got guts,
owing me money!

462
00:18:33,274 --> 00:18:34,274
Massage my back.

463
00:18:35,351 --> 00:18:37,158
That’s what I’m talking about, see!

464
00:18:37,322 --> 00:18:39,444
- That’s it!
- There you go! Do it right, do it right!

465
00:18:39,539 --> 00:18:40,845
Sorry, sorry, sorry!

466
00:18:41,387 --> 00:18:42,654
Don’t be too harsh!

467
00:18:42,844 --> 00:18:44,443
- This... feels good.
- Tso K...

468
00:18:44,468 --> 00:18:46,243
On the left, here! Press harder,
press harder there!

469
00:18:46,268 --> 00:18:47,268
Here, here, here!

470
00:18:48,001 --> 00:18:49,627
This is all our fault, Kuya.

471
00:18:50,331 --> 00:18:52,625
If it weren’t for the
supplies we had to pick up,

472
00:18:52,649 --> 00:18:54,884
Dad wouldn’t have
gotten involved.

473
00:18:55,411 --> 00:18:57,885
Tash, Dad didn’t know
the car was stolen.

474
00:18:57,998 --> 00:18:58,998
So…

475
00:18:59,239 --> 00:19:01,199
I know it’s hard to believe,

476
00:19:01,794 --> 00:19:04,401
but even my Tso K
is just a victim.

477
00:19:05,762 --> 00:19:06,762
You know what,

478
00:19:06,857 --> 00:19:08,771
don’t worry, guys.

479
00:19:09,052 --> 00:19:10,166
As they say,

480
00:19:10,801 --> 00:19:13,074
“the fruit will set you free.”

481
00:19:14,236 --> 00:19:15,236
What fruit?!

482
00:19:15,826 --> 00:19:16,826
The truth!

483
00:19:17,734 --> 00:19:20,401
Boss Beauty,
it’s the thought that counts!

484
00:19:20,459 --> 00:19:22,042
You know, just stay over
there and find your brain.

485
00:19:22,066 --> 00:19:23,931
- You’re not helping.
- I am helping.

486
00:19:24,105 --> 00:19:29,071
We need to go to the station
and save Kuya Aga.

487
00:19:29,098 --> 00:19:30,704
- Oh...
- That’s right, that’s right!

488
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:34,710
Tash, Mom called earlier and
told us not to go there, okay?

489
00:19:35,426 --> 00:19:38,326
What do you mean,
leave Dad in jail?

490
00:19:38,633 --> 00:19:39,633
Wow.

491
00:19:42,924 --> 00:19:44,244
I’ve got an idea!

492
00:19:45,219 --> 00:19:46,219
I know!

493
00:19:47,447 --> 00:19:50,354
We’ll break Kuya Aga
out of jail!

494
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:52,180
I know how to climb it!

495
00:19:52,646 --> 00:19:55,052
Guys, let’s be serious, please!

496
00:19:55,914 --> 00:19:56,987
- Please!
- Alright, alright, alright.

497
00:19:57,374 --> 00:19:59,607
Let’s be serious.
I’ve got an idea.

498
00:19:59,940 --> 00:20:00,940
Okay?

499
