I don’t really know... hard?

524
00:20:55,891 --> 00:20:58,167
Come on! You don’t know
how to massage?!

525
00:20:58,192 --> 00:21:00,240
- No, I don’t!
- Just like this, oh! Isn’t it hard? Oh.

526
00:21:00,381 --> 00:21:01,508
It’s hard like this...

527
00:21:01,665 --> 00:21:03,672
Then, massage the...

