No malice in that!

533
00:21:10,116 --> 00:21:11,116
It’s too good, Tso K.

534
00:21:11,141 --> 00:21:12,753
- Yeah, but no malice in it.
- None.

535
00:21:12,778 --> 00:21:14,171
It’s just a massage,
just a massage.

536
00:21:14,626 --> 00:21:17,466
Oh, down!
Okay... up!

537
00:21:17,732 --> 00:21:19,792
Wait, Tso K... your BFF.

538
00:21:20,391 --> 00:21:21,391
What about my BFF?

539
00:21:21,484 --> 00:21:22,724
