596
00:23:34,998 --> 00:23:35,998
Okay.

597
00:23:37,252 --> 00:23:38,412
Go on, wear it now!

598
00:23:39,100 --> 00:23:40,100
Come on, wear it!

599
00:23:43,361 --> 00:23:44,693
- Iskineport.
- Hmm?

600
00:23:44,718 --> 00:23:45,798
I have the saw here.

601
