for cowards in our group!

609
00:24:03,528 --> 00:24:04,862
No cowards allowed!

610
00:24:04,950 --> 00:24:06,790
- We’re all brave!
- No cowards allowed!

611
00:24:07,114 --> 00:24:08,228
No cowards.

612
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:09,583
No cowards!

613
00:24:09,832 --> 00:24:10,832
No cowards!

614
