- See!

760
00:29:40,057 --> 00:29:41,726
Well, we could’ve left, but you got caught!

761
00:29:41,855 --> 00:29:43,202
You move too slow!

762
00:29:43,621 --> 00:29:45,308
I didn’t know he was
coming back so soon!

763
00:29:45,333 --> 00:29:46,512
I told you to hurry up!

764
00:29:46,711 --> 00:29:47,711
I just went to the bathroom—

765
00:29:49,308 --> 00:29:50,628
- It took too long!
- Get in, get in!

766
00:29:50,861 --> 00:29:51,861
Get in.

767
00:29:52,003 --> 00:29:54,137
Alright, welcome to the club!

768
00:30:00,144 --> 00:30:02,464
Sir, we weren’t really going
to break them out, okay!

769
00:30:02,489 --> 00:30:03,669
See you in ten years!

770
00:30:04,064 --> 00:30:06,558
- Oh man! This is crazy.
- Right?!

771
00:30:06,583 --> 00:30:08,690
Yeah, it’s too much!

772
00:30:08,715 --> 00:30:09,715
Hey, mate!

773
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:10,969
I didn’t know
you were already out!

774
00:30:10,994 --> 00:30:11,994
Yeah, I made bail.

775
00:30:12,019 --> 00:30:15,490
Bail?! That’s great,
stop with your bad habits, alright?!

776
00:30:18,475 --> 00:30:21,648
Dad, we’re so happy you’re home.

777
00:30:22,274 --> 00:30:24,814
I was so surprised
you got home so early.

778
00:30:26,722 --> 00:30:27,722
Dad.

779
00:30:28,547 --> 00:30:29,547
Andres.

780
00:30:29,572 --> 00:30:30,572
I’m sorry.

781
00:30:31,165 --> 00:30:32,911
Why are you apologizing?

782
00:30:32,936 --> 00:30:35,708
Because if it weren’t for our supplies,

783
00:30:35,994 --> 00:30:38,481
you wouldn’t have gotten caught
in that carnap situation.

784
00:30:39,262 --> 00:30:42,689
No, you don’t need to apologize.

785
00:30:42,739 --> 00:30:44,306
I’ll do anything for you guys.

786
00:30:44,601 --> 00:30:47,587
And look, look at what’s happening—
the drinks are thriving!

787
00:30:48,211 --> 00:30:49,211
Look at that!

788
00:30:50,292 --> 00:30:51,292
Uncle,

789
00:30:51,317 --> 00:30:52,877
by the way, where’s Tso K?

790
00:30:52,902 --> 00:30:55,141
Oh, BFF, sorry.

791
00:30:55,166 --> 00:30:56,166
You know,

792
00:30:57,299 --> 00:30:59,346
he made a way
for me to make bail.

793
00:31:00,287 --> 00:31:02,527
He took the fall for me.

794
00:31:03,262 --> 00:31:04,496
That’s why he’s still there right now.

795
00:31:05,082 --> 00:31:06,368
- What?!
- Huh?

796
00:31:06,393 --> 00:31:07,448
You didn’t escape?

797
00:31:08,170 --> 00:31:09,170
Escape? No.

798
00:31:09,195 --> 00:31:10,207
Why would we escape?

799
00:31:10,232 --> 00:31:11,311
Uh…um…

800
00:31:11,336 --> 00:31:12,513
- What’s going on?
- Um,

801
00:31:12,891 --> 00:31:18,533
Uncle Iskineport planned
a mission to break you out?

802
00:31:18,558 --> 00:31:20,402
- Iskine—
- Hold on, hold on!

803
00:31:21,011 --> 00:31:25,051
If they’re not here,
does that mean their mission failed?

804
00:31:25,668 --> 00:31:27,742
Maybe they’re still in jail, my love!

805
00:31:28,939 --> 00:31:30,206
Oh here! Here they are!

806
00:31:30,231 --> 00:31:31,231
Hey!

807
00:31:31,511 --> 00:31:32,639
- There they are!
- My goodness, Kuya Aga!

808
00:31:32,664 --> 00:31:33,793
Tso K!

809
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:35,662
- There!
- Kuya Aga!

810
00:31:36,368 --> 00:31:38,354
- Success!
- What happened?!

811
00:31:38,423 --> 00:31:39,797
You didn’t say
you were here already!

812
00:31:39,822 --> 00:31:42,918
We went to the station
to break you out!

813
00:31:42,943 --> 00:31:44,604
Iskineport even made an effort!

814
00:31:44,779 --> 00:31:48,812
Well, thank you, thank you,
but there’s nothing. Here’s BFF!

815
00:31:48,970 --> 00:31:53,077
Good thing they caught
the real carnapper!

816
00:31:53,119 --> 00:31:54,332
Or we’d be doomed!

817
00:31:54,357 --> 00:31:56,221
- What was the name?
- Speter Spine!

818
00:31:56,705 --> 00:31:57,705
Speter Spine?

819
00:31:57,730 --> 00:32:00,427
That’s the real name?
Speter Spine?

820
00:32:00,756 --> 00:32:01,756
Wait a minute.

821
00:32:01,781 --> 00:32:04,885
What’s important is
you all got home safely.

822
00:32:06,254 --> 00:32:10,181
True! But I’m starving!

823
00:32:10,677 --> 00:32:13,329
And I’m so thirsty!

824
00:32:13,707 --> 00:32:14,873
You guys are unbelievable!

825
00:32:14,930 --> 00:32:15,930
Hungry?

826
00:32:16,102 --> 00:32:18,363
Thirsty?
That’s no problem!

827
00:32:18,547 --> 00:32:19,547
I’ve got you covered!

828
00:32:20,783 --> 00:32:21,783
There we go!

829
00:32:23,883 --> 00:32:25,250
You’re the best, BFF!

830
00:32:25,275 --> 00:32:26,443
Let’s all eat!

831
00:32:29,668 --> 00:32:30,741
Let’s sit here!

832
00:32:31,147 --> 00:32:32,147
Yeah!

833
00:32:32,172 --> 00:32:35,358
Bake K Naman,
I’ll take care of it!

834
00:32:36,286 --> 00:32:37,352
Eat, eat!

835
00:32:38,314 --> 00:32:39,948
One cheese roll, please!

836
00:32:39,973 --> 00:32:40,973
Cheese roll, oh!

837
00:32:40,998 --> 00:32:42,031
Why there?!

838
00:32:42,218 --> 00:32:43,740
- Huh?!
- No, here!

839
00:32:43,765 --> 00:32:44,765
Why there?!

840
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:47,508
It’s better here!
It’s fun here and it’s free!

841
00:32:48,816 --> 00:32:50,609
But you just said it’s on you!

842
00:32:50,693 --> 00:32:53,053
Yeah, it’s on me!
It’s on me to give it away!

843
00:32:53,123 --> 00:32:54,950
Oh, you’re such a trickster!

844
00:32:55,203 --> 00:32:57,171
Wait a minute,
have you paid here yet?

845
00:32:57,204 --> 00:32:58,204
Let’s go!

846
00:32:58,229 --> 00:33:00,439
Move over there!
Move over there!

847
00:33:00,650 --> 00:33:01,890
So I can earn something!

848
00:33:02,234 --> 00:33:03,234
It’s free here!

849
00:33:03,259 --> 00:33:04,619
I’m charging all of you!

850
00:33:05,157 --> 00:33:06,591
Come on, come on!

851
00:33:11,273 --> 00:33:18,105
Oh, just a heads-up, don’t miss the
grand reopening of Bake Haus of U, huh!

852
00:33:22,179 --> 00:33:23,652
Thank you, thank you!

853
00:33:24,117 --> 00:33:25,723
Congratulations, Kuya Aga!

854
00:33:25,860 --> 00:33:29,148
At least your hard work paid
off, and you’ve leveled up!

855
00:33:29,202 --> 00:33:30,495
Thank you, thank you!

856
00:33:35,113 --> 00:33:39,881
And of course, none of this would’ve
been possible without help from the family—

857
00:33:40,150 --> 00:33:41,210
Lola Maxi,

858
00:33:43,393 --> 00:33:44,427
Andres,

859
00:33:46,768 --> 00:33:48,527
and Atasha!

860
00:33:49,427 --> 00:33:50,427
Ate Cha!

861
00:33:50,884 --> 00:33:52,031
Don’t forget about us, too...

862
00:33:52,107 --> 00:33:55,561
Of course, you’re included!
You’re family, too!

863
00:33:55,586 --> 00:33:57,363
We really are, Ate Cha?

864
00:33:57,414 --> 00:33:58,515
Why are you acting like that?

865
00:33:58,540 --> 00:33:59,724
Oh no, we’re just really close.

866
00:34:00,732 --> 00:34:02,286
Ah, ah! What’s this?!

867
00:34:03,230 --> 00:34:04,303
- Oh no!
- Move, move!

868
00:34:04,398 --> 00:34:05,471
Move, move! Out of the way!

869
00:34:05,705 --> 00:34:06,705
Get out of the way!

870
00:34:08,697 --> 00:34:09,810
Wow!

871
00:34:11,862 --> 00:34:12,876
Hey Chef K!

872
00:34:14,136 --> 00:34:15,521
- Tso K?!
- Tso K?!

873
00:34:16,012 --> 00:34:17,066
Why are you dressed like that?

874
00:34:17,677 --> 00:34:19,624
- What’s going on?!
- Why?

875
00:34:19,649 --> 00:34:20,982
Why are you riding a motorbike?

876
00:34:21,595 --> 00:34:22,595
I’m feeling lazy.

877
00:34:22,815 --> 00:34:23,815
Why are you so concerned?

878
00:34:24,481 --> 00:34:26,228
Oh, nothing.
I’m just saying. Go ahead.

879
00:34:26,614 --> 00:34:27,614
It’s fine.

880
00:34:27,737 --> 00:34:29,717
I just wanted to take
a stroll in the park!

881
00:34:29,871 --> 00:34:31,418
Want to test drive?

882
00:34:31,603 --> 00:34:32,870
- This? No thanks.
- Yeah!

883
00:34:33,096 --> 00:34:34,580
- Why?
- I’ve learned my lesson.

884
00:34:35,077 --> 00:34:35,397
Why?

885
00:34:35,422 --> 00:34:37,557
I don’t want to risk it!
What if something happens again?!

886
00:34:37,582 --> 00:34:39,741
- Hey! I didn’t win this from a raffle!
- What?!

887
00:34:39,952 --> 00:34:41,798
I bought this myself!

888
00:34:41,976 --> 00:34:43,322
Wow!

889
00:34:46,532 --> 00:34:47,532
Hands up!

890
00:34:48,972 --> 00:34:49,972
Not you!

891
00:34:50,255 --> 00:34:51,255
Hands up!

892
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,688
- Now wh–
- This?

893
00:34:52,713 --> 00:34:54,101
- Hey Tso K!
- Me?

894
00:34:54,243 --> 00:34:56,243
You’re under arrest for fencing!

895
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:58,156
- Huh?!
- Fencing?

896
00:34:58,181 --> 00:35:00,986
Although you did buy this bike,
some parts of it were stolen!

897
00:35:01,715 --> 00:35:03,015
I’m not joking!

898
00:35:03,358 --> 00:35:05,345
I really bought it;
I didn’t do anything wrong!

899
00:35:05,370 --> 00:35:06,538
Wait, wait, wait, boss!

900
00:35:06,847 --> 00:35:07,847
Just a moment, okay?

901
00:35:08,759 --> 00:35:10,219
What happened?
I told you!

902
00:35:10,244 --> 00:35:11,244
I bought it!

903
00:35:11,356 --> 00:35:13,649
How was I supposed to know
about these stolen parts?!

904
00:35:13,975 --> 00:35:14,975
Come here.

905
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,743
Wait a second,
wait a second, boss!

906
00:35:16,768 --> 00:35:18,050
Where are we going?

907
00:35:19,109 --> 00:35:20,422
- Where are we going?
- You’re going to jail!

908
00:35:20,469 --> 00:35:21,530
- How come?
- Just wait,

909
00:35:21,554 --> 00:35:23,394
before you go to jail, let’s…

910
00:35:24,881 --> 00:35:26,307
Always remember,

911
00:35:27,106 --> 00:35:34,013
in struggles and in happiness,
Pers is the first, Pers is the hero!

912
00:35:36,301 --> 00:35:37,301
Thank you!

913
00:35:37,926 --> 00:35:39,238
- BFF!
- Oh?

914
00:35:39,263 --> 00:35:40,263
Let’s go, let’s go.

915
00:35:40,288 --> 00:35:41,288
Hang on! Why?

916
00:35:41,305 --> 00:35:43,071
Hang on! Why just me?!
I’m taking you with me!

917
00:35:43,096 --> 00:35:45,066
Come on!
Your cellmates are waiting!

918
00:35:46,290 --> 00:35:47,290
Babye!
